your different networks.

00:37:37.170 --> 00:37:40.950
Secondly, we help you get
the most value for your ads,

00:37:40.950 --> 00:37:43.980
because with Open Bidding,
all your different partners

00:37:43.980 --> 00:37:47.640
are going to compete for
the inventory simultaneously

00:37:47.640 --> 00:37:49.600
and in real time.

00:37:49.600 --> 00:37:51.780
