00:42:45.920 --> 00:42:48.100
So stay up to date in your
understanding of what's

00:42:48.100 --> 00:42:49.190
going on the platform.

00:42:52.060 --> 00:42:54.090
The most obvious
and the biggest one

00:42:54.090 --> 00:42:59.610
